---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import CtaBand from '../components/CtaBand.astro';
import LandscapeAccent from '../components/LandscapeAccent.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Our Process | Canyon Strategic Wealth"
  description="A structured, transparent onboarding — six phases from your first conversation to an ongoing, year-round planning partnership."
>
  <div class="page-header">
    <h1>Our Process</h1>
    <p>A structured, transparent onboarding experience — from your first conversation to ongoing partnership.</p>
  </div>

  <LandscapeAccent
    src="/landscapes/wasatch-rocky.jpg"
    alt="The canyon walls of the Wasatch front"
    height="220px"
    position="center 40%"
  />

  <section class="section">
    <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:48px;">
      <div class="section-eyebrow dark">The Journey</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Six Phases to Your Financial Confidence</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle" style="margin:0 auto;">Each phase builds on the last, creating a comprehensive strategy that covers every dimension of your financial life.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="process-timeline">
      <div class="process-step fade-in">
        <div class="process-dot">1</div>
        <div class="process-content">
          <h3>Intro &amp; Discovery</h3>
          <div class="process-timing">Weeks 1–2</div>
          <p>We get to know each other and gather the full picture of your financial life — income, assets, liabilities, goals, and what matters most to you.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step fade-in">
        <div class="process-dot">2</div>
        <div class="process-content">
          <h3>Roadmap &amp; Alignment</h3>
          <div class="process-timing">Weeks 2–3</div>
          <p>Our team builds your personalized financial plan — a strategic roadmap of priorities. We review it together and align on direction before moving forward.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step fade-in">
        <div class="process-dot">3</div>
        <div class="process-content">
          <h3>Implementation</h3>
          <div class="process-timing">Weeks 3–5</div>
          <p>Planning turns into action — opening accounts, transferring assets, establishing positions, and setting everything in motion.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step fade-in">
        <div class="process-dot">4</div>
        <div class="process-content">
          <h3>Optimization</h3>
          <div class="process-timing">Weeks 5–8</div>
          <p>We tie investments, tax strategy, and cash flow together. Your CPA joins the team so everything works holistically and tax-efficiently.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step fade-in">
        <div class="process-dot">5</div>
        <div class="process-content">
          <h3>Integration</h3>
          <div class="process-timing">Weeks 8–12</div>
          <p>We protect your wealth through estate planning and risk management, coordinate with your professional team, and stress-test for the unexpected.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step fade-in">
        <div class="process-dot">6</div>
        <div class="process-content">
          <h3>Ongoing Partnership</h3>
          <div class="process-timing">Always</div>
          <p>You move into our annual rhythm — biannual planning meetings, proactive check-in calls, and year-round coordination across your entire professional team.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-dark">
    <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:48px;position:relative;z-index:2;">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">Year-Round Partnership</div>
      <h2 class="section-title light">Your Annual Rhythm</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle light" style="margin:0 auto;">Beyond the initial onboarding, we maintain a proactive engagement model throughout the year to keep everything aligned.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="ongoing-grid">
      <div class="ongoing-card">
        <div class="ongoing-season"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22V8" /><path d="M5 12s2-4 7-4 7 4 7 4" /><path d="M7 6s2-3 5-3 5 3 5 3" /><path d="M12 8c0-3 2-5 2-5" /><path d="M12 8c0-3-2-5-2-5" /></svg></div>
        <h4>Spring Meeting</h4>
        <div class="ongoing-type">Full Review</div>
        <p>Plan updates, progress on action items, investment review, tax positioning, and any life changes since we last met.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="ongoing-card">
        <div class="ongoing-season"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="5" /><line x1="12" y1="1" x2="12" y2="3" /><line x1="12" y1="21" x2="12" y2="23" /><line x1="4.22" y1="4.22" x2="5.64" y2="5.64" /><line x1="18.36" y1="18.36" x2="19.78" y2="19.78" /><line x1="1" y1="12" x2="3" y2="12" /><line x1="21" y1="12" x2="23" y2="12" /><line x1="4.22" y1="19.78" x2="5.64" y2="18.36" /><line x1="18.36" y1="5.64" x2="19.78" y2="4.22" /></svg></div>
        <h4>Summer Call</h4>
        <div class="ongoing-type">Check-In</div>
        <p>Proactive lighter-touch call to surface any emerging needs, share quick updates, and stay connected.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="ongoing-card">
        <div class="ongoing-season"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M11 20A7 7 0 019.8 6.9C15.5 4.9 17 3.5 19 2c1 2 2 4.5 2 8 0 5.5-4.5 10-10 10z" /><path d="M2 21c0-3 1.85-5.36 5.08-6C9.5 14.52 12 13 13 12" /></svg></div>
        <h4>Fall Meeting</h4>
        <div class="ongoing-type">Year-End Planning</div>
        <p>Tax-loss harvesting, Roth conversions, charitable giving, insurance renewals, and goal-setting for the year ahead.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="ongoing-card">
        <div class="ongoing-season"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="12" y1="2" x2="12" y2="22" /><line x1="2" y1="12" x2="22" y2="12" /><line x1="4.93" y1="4.93" x2="19.07" y2="19.07" /><line x1="19.07" y1="4.93" x2="4.93" y2="19.07" /><line x1="9" y1="2" x2="12" y2="5" /><line x1="15" y1="2" x2="12" y2="5" /><line x1="9" y1="22" x2="12" y2="19" /><line x1="15" y1="22" x2="12" y2="19" /></svg></div>
        <h4>Winter Call</h4>
        <div class="ongoing-type">Year-End Wrap-Up</div>
        <p>Confirm final actions, personal connection, and make sure nothing slips through the cracks before the new year.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <CtaBand
    heading="Start Your Journey Today"
    text="The first step is a simple conversation."
    ctaLabel="Schedule Your Discovery Call"
  />
</BaseLayout>
